data.description: Welcome home! This charming single level home in Admirals Cove offers the best of open-concept living. Enjoy sipping coffee on your front porch in the morning while taking in the sweeping southern views of Admiralty Inlet, the Olympic Mountains, Crockett Lake Preserve, the Coupeville Ferry, and Fort Casey State Park. Kitchen opens to dining room and living room, has slider to fenced-in back yard, plenty of storage. Brand new paint and carpet throughout. Enjoy 3 spacious bedrooms plus office off entry (2 bedroom septic). Primary suite has large bathroom, walk-in closet. Admirals Cove offers beach club is optional for membership with pool, clubhouse, beach access. Don't miss the chance to be on vacation every day in this stunning property!
